Currently Implemented GoodDollar Flow:
---------------------------------------
-Create a wallet ---> Enter details (Full Name) ----> Phone verification
-Login ---> Enter seed phrase ---> Main app page (landing)


========================================================

User Scenarios
---------------

Basic 

-Initial Account Creation
-User with GoodDollar account (signing in)
-New user verifying identity
-User wants to edit identity
-User wants to remove identity

Exception Scenarios

-User forgot their PIN
-User with rejected approval
-User with existing GoodDollar attempting to register
  -User with existing IdentityRegistry attempting to register
  -(NOTE: Leave this out for now)
  -(Loose assumption that GoodDollar is the only one connected to IdentityRegistry (we live in GoodDollar land!))

Security Scenarios

-Malicious user attempting to enter existing GoodDollar (attack on recovery option)


========================================================


Prospective Flow:
------------------

============================  
Basic
============================

Initial Account Creation

  Create Account ---> Choose a PIN ---> (Optional) Fingerprint/FaceID? (mobile) ---> Enter minimal details (Full Name, Email) ---> Account Landing Page 

===

Log-in Process (signing in)

  Main Landing Page ---> Enter PIN (or Fingerprint/FaceID) ---> Account Landing Page

===

Identity Verification for User (New user verifying identity)

  Account Landing Page ---> (Action that triggers/forces identity) ---> Identity (address, all information, ID card*, camera image (e.g. holding paper with timestamp)**) and account verification text boxes (Facebook/LinkedIn/Twitter [ Verify (button)*** ]) ---> Approval sent!****

  * Mini-flow of ID Document Verification

    Brief Instructions and Select an ID type (Driver's license, ID card, Passport) ---> Select an upload method (Webcam/Mobile Camera (a), File Upload (b)) ---> Next

      a. Webcam/Mobile Camera
        Instructions on Photo (e.g. ID card in line with square borders) and Camera Screen ---> Use this photo? (can be in same modal/screen) ---> Next

      b. File Upload
        Brief instructions on file upload, click/drag image ---> Use this image? ---> Next

  ** Mini-flow of Photo Identity Verification

    Brief Instructions and Select an upload method (Webcam/Mobile Camera (a), File Upload (b)) ---> Next

      a. Webcam/Mobile Camera
        Instructions on Photo (e.g. face in camera) and Camera Screen ---> Use this photo? (can be in same modal/screen) ---> Next

      b. File Upload
        Brief instructions on file upload, click/drag image ---> Use this image? ---> Next


  *** Mini-flow of Individual Account Verification

    [ Verify ] ---> Instructions page ---> (in new tab) Path for doing on-platform verifying (such as tweeting a unique code) ---> Enter details page

  (Extra note)
  **** Send email confirming approval sending, and give seed phrase. At this point, the user has an account on GoodDollar, simply not approved (and can access approval status in this way)


