============================  
Exception Scenarios
============================

User forgot their PIN

  Main Landing Page ---> Log In (forgot your PIN?) ---> Options (Restore account with seed backup*, Contact support**) 

  * Mini-flow of Seed Backup
  
    Enter Seed ---> Enter a new PIN ---> Success! Try logging in again ---> Log in page (perhaps redirect) 

  ** Mini-flow of Contact Support
   
    Restore Account Support Instructions and Information ("Contact us at support@gooddollar.org to... Please provide the following: ")

===

User with rejected approval

  Main Landing Page ---> Log In ---> Main Landing Page ---> Identity Verification (status, resend approval) ---> Review details (Revise*, Submit) ---> Approval re-sent! 

  * Mini-flow of Identity Approval Revision

    Revise information (fields filled in with last approval's data) ---> Review details (Revise*, Submit)

===

User with existing GoodDollar attempting to register

  Create Account ---> Choose a PIN ---> (Optional) Fingerprint/FaceID? (mobile) ---> Enter minimal details (Full Name, Email) ---> Already in our system! (Login*, Restore account**)

  * Mini-flow of entire "Log in" scenario
  ** Mini-flow of entire "User forgot their PIN" scenario



